A Blueberry Muffin Session Pastry Porter. Omnishambles was brewed with freshly baked blueberry muffins from our Bakeshop before being conditioned on even more blueberry muffins, Tahitiian vanilla beans, and a touch of Ceylon cinnamon. Big, inviting notes of jammy blueberry, rich vanilla, and sweet shortcrust mix with a soft roast character adding tones of chocolatey mocha and crumb topping. Think slice of blueberry pie on a summer picnic vibes. 7.5%.

MONSTROUS shoutout to the Wandering Monsters crew, we had so much fun with this one! Find Omnishambles at our locations in Athens + Columbus now and stay tuned for its debut in Cincinnati coming soon. Cheers! 

#wanderingmonsters #jackieosbrewery #pastry #porter #collabbeer".
